@node OptionsR1


## R ##


It scans recursively, that's to say in all subdrawers.

Note : the 't' option of MPTool 0.04 is similar to -RL


                            @{" Back To The Options " link Options}  


@endnode
@node Optionss


## s ##


It forces MPTool to show empty TAG fields.


CLI>c:MPTool -azZ sd0:

 ===========================[MPTool]===['98ÀTMGÀ]===============================

